summary: Working on a tribute to Stan Lee.  Sketch phase right now.   Things are slow but they’ll pick up so I can have it finished this...
body: Working on a tribute to Stan Lee. Sketch phase right now. Things are slow but they’ll pick up so I can have it finished this week. I normally don’t do this type of thing but I do feel I am obligated in this case since he was the biggest reason I got into drawing in the first place. As a kid, the first hero I ever drew was Spider-man (granted it was a red and blue stick figure but dammit I knew I drew Spidey)!

summary: I'm selling fakemon I don't use or want anymore and hoping to find good homes for the fakes I draw. Here's another fakemon that...
caption:
I’m selling fakemon I don’t use or want anymore and hoping to find good homes for the fakes I draw. Here’s another fakemon that I don’t intend on using for any region or future region that I plan to make.
These fakemon are just spiked fish fakemon, somewhat based off Piranhas and Spikes obviously. To buy these fakemon, it just costs 30$, PayPal only, and it goes to the first person who comments wanting to purchase this fakemon. Once bought, I will send you a note with a link to my PayPal, and I will send you the file with the fakemon once I receive payment. You can choose to receive the file as a SAI file or a PSD File. Either works for me


This fakemon is also over on deviantart https://www.deviantart.com/deku93/art/Another-Sell-772767763

If this fakemon sells here, I’ll update the deviantart post, or if it sells there, I’ll delete this or post an update.

blog.description: I'm an aspiring artist with ADHD and a million ideas in my head. I started out with mostly pokemon but have since then spreaded my horizons. I do still draw pokemon, but also draw anthros and whatever comes to mind. Still need to get back into drawing comics though. I'd love any help or suggestions you can give to help me improve more! Any support is always greatly appreciated!! Currently applying for SVA in Manhattan New York City for animation. Also check out my PMD comic and my upcoming original comic!
